Package production

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Item
    Item interface that is implemented by Product.
    MultimediaControl
    Interface MultimediaControl that AudioPlayer and MoviePlayer implement.
    ScreenSpec
    Interface that Screen implements to get specifications about the Screen.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AudioPlayer
    AudioPlayer class that extends Product and implements MultimediaControl.
    AudioPlayerDriver
    Driver class for the AudioPlayer class.
    Controller
    Controller class that handles the logic for the GUI to Database relationship.
    Employee  
    Main
    Main class for the JavaFX GUI 'start' method and displays the GUI.
    MoviePlayer
    MoviePlayer class that extends Product and implements MultimediaControl.
    Product
    Abstract class that implements Item and represents a Product that can be produced.
    ProductionRecord
    Represents a record when a Product is produced.
    Screen
    Represents a Screen on a MoviePlayer.
    Widget
    Represents a new Product object.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ItemType
    ItemType enumeration that holds what type of item the created Product is.
    MonitorType
    MonitorType enumeration for holding the type of screen the product has.
